snippet.title: Pikmin S Trailer 1
snippet.description:
Pikmin S is a full story mode hack for Pikmin 2, and features new Pikmin types, elements, treasures and much more!!

To learn more about Pikmin S, join the Discord update server: https://discord.gg/NUWksAjFwz

this project has no approximated release date, depending on development time, modeling and other unforeseen events.

Thank you for looking forward to Pikmin S!
